1
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:39,657
[Episode 11]

2
00:01:39,657 --> 00:01:42,640
Zhang Yue! If you fail to capture those two,

3
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:46,505
I'll make everyone in Hanshui Palace
be buried with them!

4
00:01:55,519 --> 00:01:58,519
Huo Xiao Mei? You arrived just in time.

5
00:01:58,519 --> 00:01:59,760
Use your advantage.

6
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:01,079
Lead her away.

7
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:04,317
Miss Huo. Be careful of the Love Longing.

8
00:02:09,338 --> 00:02:13,320
We can't keep fighting like this.
We must find a way to escape.

9
00:02:13,320 --> 00:02:14,719
Capture Zhi Hua.

10
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:17,023
Use him as a hostage.

11
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:43,380
What a bunch of useless fools.

12
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:53,800
Is that all the power your
'Little Compassion Palm' has?

13
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:56,192
Did you and Zhi Hua share the same master?

14
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:57,880
I won't dodge this time.

15
00:02:57,880 --> 00:03:00,555
Come on, hit me right here.

16
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:10,633
Love Longing and Yin Yang An
are both forged from magnets.

17
00:03:10,633 --> 00:03:13,517
Fighting like this won't benefit anyone.

18
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:23,479
Hanshui Palace has been secluded for years.

19
00:03:23,479 --> 00:03:24,999
Why have you become Zhi Hua's accomplice?

20
00:03:24,999 --> 00:03:26,599
This is not our intention.

21
00:03:26,599 --> 00:03:28,917
You're being threatened by Zhi Hua?

22
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:33,780
Where's Xiao Di? How is he?

23
00:03:33,780 --> 00:03:37,316
- Xiao Di--
- Everyone, stop!

24
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:54,046
If you don't stop now,

25
00:03:54,046 --> 00:03:57,167
I'll slit the throat of this
'Little Compassion Palm'.

26
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:10,559
Zhi Hua!

27
00:04:10,559 --> 00:04:11,920
What are you doing now?

28
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:13,399
If you make another move,

29
00:04:13,399 --> 00:04:15,680
I'll really do it.

30
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,960
Zhi Hua!

31
00:04:17,960 --> 00:04:19,080
If I die...

32
00:04:19,080 --> 00:04:21,555
how will you answer to He Bo?

33
00:04:21,555 --> 00:04:24,392
Exactly. How will you explain it?

34
00:04:25,439 --> 00:04:27,224
Move aside!

35
00:04:47,399 --> 00:04:49,959
Murder!

36
00:05:19,839 --> 00:05:22,492
I didn't expect you to be so useful.

37
00:05:23,599 --> 00:05:24,760
After them!

38
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:26,705
Stop right there!

39
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:46,719
It's all thanks to Shen Zhong Yuan.

40
00:05:46,719 --> 00:05:49,559
I finally got to eat Linglong Honey.

41
00:05:49,559 --> 00:05:53,705
Shen Zhong Yuan's Pili Palm is not
just an empty reputation.

42
00:05:53,705 --> 00:05:57,310
Don't use your inner strength
for the next few days.

43
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,400
That kick of yours was quite brutal.

44
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:04,840
Tell me the truth.
Was that a personal vendetta?

45
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,180
- Yes.
- You...

46
00:06:06,180 --> 00:06:07,667
Zhan.

47
00:06:08,367 --> 00:06:10,160
Is your wound bandaged?

48
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,600
I'm fine.

49
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,746
It's just a superficial wound. Don't worry.

50
00:06:13,746 --> 00:06:15,067
I'm hurt too.

51
00:06:15,067 --> 00:06:16,630
Right here. He kicked me.

52
00:06:16,630 --> 00:06:18,730
Didn't you just have Linglong Honey?

53
00:06:20,519 --> 00:06:22,942
Did you see Miss Yu Lian?

54
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:26,406
Many girls are indeed locked up there.

55
00:06:26,406 --> 00:06:28,453
But I didn't see Yu Lian.

56
00:06:28,453 --> 00:06:30,160
I heard from one of the girls

57
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:33,126
that she's with He Bo, the
owner of Zhongxiao Pavilion.

58
00:06:33,126 --> 00:06:34,360
She doesn't appear often.

59
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:36,680
Are they all right?

60
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,600
They're trapped in a mire,

61
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,467
struggling to survive.

62
00:06:43,280 --> 00:06:47,400
How did you find out that Zhan Zhao and I were
in danger at Zhongxiao Pavilion?

63
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:48,800
Zhan, you were right.

64
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:51,117
Hua Chong is indeed suspicious.

65
00:06:53,038 --> 00:06:54,280
[Fenglai Pavilion]

66
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:55,840
Master Hua, you're leaving?

67
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:57,319
- Leaving so early this time?
- I'll come for you tomorrow.

68
00:06:57,319 --> 00:06:59,555
- All right.
- Come back soon!

69
00:07:10,192 --> 00:07:11,480
[Ruzhen Embroidery Shop]

70
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:13,692
Has anything strange happened lately?

71
00:07:13,692 --> 00:07:17,240
Well, three people with
strange behavior showed up.

72
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,600
Two men and one woman.

73
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:21,167
They even broke into the backyard.

74
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:24,179
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

75
00:07:24,179 --> 00:07:26,920
Do you have any idea how much
trouble you've caused me?

76
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,855
What's wrong, Master Hua?

77
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,119
I'm unwell.

78
00:07:33,119 --> 00:07:37,355
- Where exactly are you feeling ill?
- Don't ask too many questions.

79
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:40,492
Keep a low profile for a few days.

80
00:07:40,492 --> 00:07:43,230
I won't be bringing any girls here for now.

81
00:07:43,230 --> 00:07:45,313
Can you be more careful?

82
00:07:45,313 --> 00:07:48,617
Don't let anything else go wrong, okay?

83
00:07:48,617 --> 00:07:51,199
Master Hua, may I ask...

84
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:52,800
who exactly were those three people?

85
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,776
You don't need to worry about that.

86
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:57,720
No matter who they are,

87
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:01,400
once they enter Zhongxiao Pavilion,

88
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:04,130
there is no coming back.

89
00:08:05,119 --> 00:08:07,320
Damn. I really underestimated that Hua Chong.

90
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:10,159
If I catch him again, I'll skin him alive!

91
00:08:10,159 --> 00:08:11,599
I've already tied him up.

92
00:08:11,599 --> 00:08:13,200
Fan is watching over him.

93
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:14,760
Not bad, Huo Xiao Mei.

94
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:16,000
Once this case is closed,

95
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:19,442
you can follow Zhan Zhao
and work at Kaifeng Prefecture.

96
00:08:22,159 --> 00:08:25,717
Who are these masters at Zhongxiao Pavilion
that could actually wound you?

97
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:29,830
After I was separated from Bai Yu Tang,

98
00:08:29,830 --> 00:08:33,599
I was led into a secret room,
and encountered three swordsmen.

99
00:08:33,599 --> 00:08:35,240
They fought with perfect coordination,

100
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:38,360
and were all controlled by
the bells in Zhi Hua's hand.

101
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:40,479
They attacked relentlessly.

102
00:08:40,479 --> 00:08:43,959
Once they pin you down, it's hard to escape.

103
00:08:43,959 --> 00:08:47,360
And the strangest thing is
the sword techniques they used...

104
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:49,800
One was the Dragon Roar Swordplay
of Bawang Manor.

105
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:51,800
Another was the Lone Shadow Swordplay
of Shengyun Manor.

106
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:56,063
And also, the Soaring Cloud Swordplay
of Linglong Manor.

107
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:58,680
It seems Zhongxiao Pavilion...

108
00:08:58,680 --> 00:09:02,730
is indeed more than just a
place of luxury and pleasure.

109
00:09:05,680 --> 00:09:06,760
Lord Zhan.

110
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:08,240
Fan.

111
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:11,640
We have confirmed that Yu Lian was indeed
taken to Zhongxiao Pavilion.

112
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:12,719
Then is she all right now?

113
00:09:12,719 --> 00:09:14,755
She is fine.

114
00:09:14,755 --> 00:09:17,919
Tonight, we really had no way to bring her out.

115
00:09:17,919 --> 00:09:19,316
But don't you worry.

116
00:09:19,316 --> 00:09:21,519
Since we've confirmed
Yu Lian is in Zhongxiao Pavilion,

117
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:23,992
we will definitely be able to save her.

118
00:09:24,980 --> 00:09:26,159
Well.

119
00:09:26,159 --> 00:09:28,240
Huo Xiao Mei was quite rough on you.

120
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,680
You've got a lot of nerve,

121
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:31,800
trying to play tricks on me.

122
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:33,959
I failed to recognize your true color before.

123
00:09:33,959 --> 00:09:37,803
What? Should I be calling you
Master Hua as well?

124
00:09:43,159 --> 00:09:44,400
Bai Yu Tang,

125
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:46,200
Be smart and let me go now. Do you hear me?

126
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,839
Otherwise... Ah!

127
00:09:47,839 --> 00:09:49,959
What? You want to hit me again?

128
00:09:49,959 --> 00:09:51,719
You've beaten me all night, crazy woman!

129
00:09:51,719 --> 00:09:53,120
You're addicted to it, aren't you?

130
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:55,360
You helped Zhongxiao Pavilion
harm so many girls.

131
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:58,067
You're lucky I didn't
just kill you with my sword.

132
00:10:03,159 --> 00:10:04,774
Kill me?

133
00:10:05,479 --> 00:10:07,617
Do you dare?

134
00:10:09,039 --> 00:10:12,080
What did that scholar call him just now?

135
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:14,292
Lord Zhan.

136
00:10:15,640 --> 00:10:17,519
- You...
- Lord...

137
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:19,855
You're with the government, aren't you?

138
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:23,240
An official...

139
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:25,880
cannot commit murder.

140
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:33,242
Help! Help--

141
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:36,760
It's all right.

142
00:10:36,760 --> 00:10:38,240
I'm not.

143
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:42,840
An inn like this is not a convenient place
to hide a living person.

144
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:44,039
Besides,

145
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:46,679
Shao Ji Zu already knows where we are.

146
00:10:46,679 --> 00:10:48,567
We must find a new place to stay.

147
00:10:48,567 --> 00:10:50,080
Lord Zhan,

148
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:51,960
I have a distant relative in this town.

149
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:54,080
He moved to the capital a few months ago.

150
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,679
His residence happens to be vacant.

151
00:10:55,679 --> 00:10:56,840
We can move there.

152
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,542
I think that's a good idea.

153
00:10:59,199 --> 00:11:01,240
Tomorrow morning, I'll prepare a donkey cart

154
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:04,240
to take Hua Chong and Fan
out through the back door.

155
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,279
Huo Xiao Mei,

156
00:11:05,279 --> 00:11:06,319
when the city gates open tomorrow,

157
00:11:06,319 --> 00:11:08,360
go with Zhan Zhao out of the city.

158
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:10,116
Leave the city?

159
00:11:12,519 --> 00:11:13,720
Master Bai,

160
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:16,017
have you caught a cold?

161
00:11:16,017 --> 00:11:18,680
Yeah, a cold.

162
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:20,080
A cold?

163
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:23,980
After finishing our business tomorrow,
go to the pharmacy for some medicine.

164
00:12:15,055 --> 00:12:17,568
[Jing Yi Ming, Master of Shangqing Sect]

165
00:12:17,568 --> 00:12:18,967
[He Bo]

166
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:41,000
[Jing Xing Ze, Shangqing Sect]

167
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,720
Father!

168
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:45,360
Zhi Hua didn't discuss tonight's plan
with me beforehand.

169
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:48,242
He caused this mess on his own.

170
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:54,360
Do you know what kind of people come to
Zhongxiao Pavilion for pleasure?

171
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:56,519
You took it upon yourself to dismiss guests,

172
00:12:56,519 --> 00:12:59,159
causing panic and leaving a total mess!

173
00:12:59,159 --> 00:13:01,917
And yet, you failed to catch anyone.

174
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:05,679
Father,

175
00:13:05,679 --> 00:13:07,640
Zhi Hua doesn't just disrespect you.

176
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:10,240
Just now, he even tried to have me killed.

177
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:12,240
Bai Yu Tang's blade was at my throat,

178
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:15,961
yet he deliberately provoked him,
hoping Bai Yu Tang would kill me.

179
00:13:19,199 --> 00:13:22,159
Regardless, disturbing the guests tonight...

180
00:13:22,159 --> 00:13:23,600
was my mistake.

181
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,769
Please punish me, Master.

182
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:31,080
Take your men.

183
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:33,360
Clean up Zhongxiao Pavilion.

184
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:36,480
Ensure it can open for business tomorrow.

185
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:39,242
Master, right now Zhan Zhao--

186
00:13:42,279 --> 00:13:43,305
Father,

187
00:13:43,305 --> 00:13:45,760
I just remembered,
I still have some matters to handle.

188
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:47,120
I'll go take care of it now.

189
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:48,692
Wait.

190
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:52,919
The invitations for the birthday
banquet were just sent out,

191
00:13:52,919 --> 00:13:55,279
but Ding Zhao Hui arrived today.

192
00:13:55,279 --> 00:13:57,640
I've arranged for him to stay at the manor.

193
00:13:57,640 --> 00:14:00,600
His early arrival is a bit suspicious.

194
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:02,840
Take a few men to keep an eye on him.

195
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,780
I understand.

196
00:14:10,399 --> 00:14:14,199
Do you think I don't know what you're planning?

197
00:14:14,199 --> 00:14:18,880
Do you think having Si Ming's support
allows you to walk all over me?

198
00:14:18,880 --> 00:14:22,319
Zhongxiao Pavilion has only one master,
and that is me, He Bo.

199
00:14:22,319 --> 00:14:25,319
Those improper thoughts of yours,

200
00:14:25,319 --> 00:14:27,755
you'd better put them away.

201
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:43,519
I told you not to use
the Great Compassion Palm lightly,

202
00:14:43,519 --> 00:14:45,439
yet you used it so recklessly.

203
00:14:45,439 --> 00:14:50,005
You want everyone to know that I taught you
the secret skills of the Shangqing Sect?

204
00:14:51,679 --> 00:14:53,480
Ruining my reputation,

205
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:56,280
what exactly do you gain from it?

206
00:14:58,760 --> 00:15:03,640
I-I never intended
to ruin your reputation, Master.

207
00:15:03,640 --> 00:15:04,799
It's just that...

208
00:15:04,799 --> 00:15:08,519
the Great Compassion Palm is the only
skill I have to protect myself.

209
00:15:08,519 --> 00:15:11,360
I've journeyed through the world for ages.

210
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:14,780
Without the Great Compassion Palm's protection,

211
00:15:14,780 --> 00:15:18,005
I would have died many times over.

212
00:15:24,919 --> 00:15:26,240
In a moment,

213
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:29,080
go and tend to your wound.

214
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:30,640
As for today's matter,

215
00:15:30,640 --> 00:15:33,600
don't blame me for losing my temper.

216
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:36,240
The birthday banquet is approaching,

217
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:38,710
yet you caused such a commotion.

218
00:15:39,399 --> 00:15:42,640
I'm afraid you'll ruin my plans.

219
00:15:42,640 --> 00:15:45,605
It was precisely for your plans...

220
00:15:45,605 --> 00:15:48,519
that I decided to strike tonight.

221
00:15:48,519 --> 00:15:51,439
Zhan Zhao found Zhongxiao Pavilion so quickly.

222
00:15:51,439 --> 00:15:54,399
I feared he'd follow the trail
and uncover even more.

223
00:15:54,399 --> 00:15:58,179
If that happened,
your decade of painstaking efforts...

224
00:15:59,159 --> 00:16:01,780
would all go down the drain.

225
00:16:04,319 --> 00:16:05,840
Good for you.

226
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:08,623
To be so considerate of me.

227
00:16:09,399 --> 00:16:14,319
Fine. Zhongxiao Pavilion will make an
exception and close for a day to reorganize.

228
00:16:14,319 --> 00:16:17,763
You go and focus on dealing with Zhan Zhao.

229
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:29,440
Once the birthday banquet is over,

230
00:16:29,440 --> 00:16:33,342
and I finish what I have to do,

231
00:16:33,342 --> 00:16:35,967
this identity as the leader
of a prestigious sect...

232
00:16:36,760 --> 00:16:39,205
I won't mind casting it aside.

233
00:16:40,799 --> 00:16:43,092
What you desire,

234
00:16:43,092 --> 00:16:46,605
I will eventually give it to you.

235
00:16:49,742 --> 00:16:52,342
I understand, Father. I understand.

236
00:16:52,342 --> 00:16:55,543
I only wish to help you
achieve your great ambition.

237
00:17:01,830 --> 00:17:04,717
Leave through the back door.
Don't let anyone see you.

238
00:17:21,039 --> 00:17:24,067
Madam, what was that?

239
00:17:27,159 --> 00:17:30,360
[Mrs. Jing, Shangqing Sect]
It was just a stray cat. Don't make a fuss.

240
00:17:30,360 --> 00:17:33,120
I will have someone
clear out the stray cats tomorrow,

241
00:17:33,120 --> 00:17:35,471
so they don't disturb your peace.

242
00:17:36,040 --> 00:17:37,286
No matter.

243
00:17:37,286 --> 00:17:40,559
That little cat
often plays in the front garden.

244
00:17:40,559 --> 00:17:44,480
It must have been greedy for food
and couldn't find its way home.

245
00:17:44,480 --> 00:17:46,480
The door to the corridor is open now.

246
00:17:46,480 --> 00:17:48,199
It only needs to walk out,

247
00:17:48,199 --> 00:17:49,519
turn a few corners,

248
00:17:49,519 --> 00:17:52,092
and it will reach the front garden.

249
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:06,447
Is there anything unusual?

250
00:18:06,447 --> 00:18:08,992
Sir, nothing unusual.

251
00:18:24,680 --> 00:18:26,330
Did you...

252
00:18:26,330 --> 00:18:28,800
see anyone just now?

253
00:18:28,800 --> 00:18:30,442
My Lord,

254
00:18:30,442 --> 00:18:34,692
I only saw a stray cat darting across the roof.

255
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:38,839
And you?

256
00:18:38,839 --> 00:18:40,120
My Lord,

257
00:18:40,120 --> 00:18:43,255
I also only saw a stray cat.

258
00:20:15,080 --> 00:20:17,199
Please! Spare my life! Spare my life!

259
00:20:17,199 --> 00:20:18,560
I didn't do it on purpose.

260
00:20:18,560 --> 00:20:21,640
They held a knife to my throat
and forced me to do it.

261
00:20:21,640 --> 00:20:24,039
Did they also hold a knife to your throat

262
00:20:24,039 --> 00:20:26,442
and force you into Zhongxiao Pavilion?

263
00:20:28,999 --> 00:20:30,992
W-W-What Pavilion?

264
00:20:30,992 --> 00:20:33,642
Don't play dumb. Start talking.

265
00:20:34,959 --> 00:20:38,305
Fine, fine. I'll talk.

266
00:20:39,160 --> 00:20:41,892
Where do you want me to start?

267
00:20:44,160 --> 00:20:45,920
Start with Yu Lian's disappearance.

268
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:47,039
Your County Magistrate,

269
00:20:47,039 --> 00:20:48,600
though he took the case,

270
00:20:48,600 --> 00:20:50,160
he was just going through the motions.

271
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:53,439
Did he already know about
the goings-on in Zhongxiao Pavilion?

272
00:20:53,439 --> 00:20:54,680
Yes.

273
00:20:54,680 --> 00:20:57,439
Lord Li frequented Zhongxiao Pavilion.

274
00:20:57,439 --> 00:20:59,640
So he knew Yu Lian had been
abducted into there.

275
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:01,999
But he never intended to investigate.

276
00:21:01,999 --> 00:21:04,319
He even warned us not to be meddlesome.

277
00:21:04,319 --> 00:21:07,455
The trade market official is also
a regular at Zhongxiao Pavilion.

278
00:21:07,455 --> 00:21:08,799
Yes.

279
00:21:08,799 --> 00:21:12,519
That trade market official often delivers
intelligence to Zhongxiao Pavilion.

280
00:21:12,519 --> 00:21:14,600
He is also an honored guest there.

281
00:21:14,600 --> 00:21:17,680
That day, he went to see Lord Li in a panic,

282
00:21:17,680 --> 00:21:20,720
saying the secret letter for He Bo
had been stolen.

283
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:22,800
Lord Li was gloating at first,

284
00:21:22,800 --> 00:21:26,370
until he realized his own token for
entering Zhongxiao Pavilion was also missing.

285
00:21:26,370 --> 00:21:28,167
So he...

286
00:21:30,239 --> 00:21:31,560
So, so...

287
00:21:31,560 --> 00:21:33,830
So he thought of Liu Hong Yi.

288
00:21:33,830 --> 00:21:37,080
Liu often opposed him and went against him.

289
00:21:37,080 --> 00:21:39,400
Liu's whereabouts were
uncertain during those days,

290
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:44,120
so Lord Li concluded that Liu had secretly
taken on Yu Lian's case,

291
00:21:44,120 --> 00:21:45,880
and used it to investigate Zhongxiao Pavilion.

292
00:21:45,880 --> 00:21:49,439
So Lord Li set a trap to arrest Liu Hong Yi.

293
00:21:49,439 --> 00:21:53,280
He also planted the missing token
in Liu's house,

294
00:21:54,840 --> 00:21:55,999
along with...

295
00:21:55,999 --> 00:21:58,145
along with the letters he exchanged with you.

296
00:21:58,145 --> 00:22:00,972
Afterward, Lord Li handed him over to He Bo.

297
00:22:00,972 --> 00:22:02,959
To save his own skin,

298
00:22:02,959 --> 00:22:06,560
Lord Li didn't mention that it was his
own negligence regarding Yu Lian's case

299
00:22:06,560 --> 00:22:09,080
that led Liu Hong Yi to Zhongxiao Pavilion.

300
00:22:09,080 --> 00:22:11,759
He simply said the trade market official
got drunk

301
00:22:11,759 --> 00:22:13,199
and talked too much at the court,

302
00:22:13,199 --> 00:22:17,092
which drew Liu Hong Yi's attention
and led to the theft of the secret letter.

303
00:22:21,759 --> 00:22:24,781
Lord Li is quite clever.

304
00:22:25,399 --> 00:22:28,199
He knew Liu would never refute his story

305
00:22:28,199 --> 00:22:30,930
to protect Yu Lian and Fan.

306
00:22:32,520 --> 00:22:33,999
You're quite clever too.

307
00:22:33,999 --> 00:22:35,320
With your smooth talk,

308
00:22:35,320 --> 00:22:37,159
you've cleared yourself of all blame.

309
00:22:37,159 --> 00:22:38,542
I...

310
00:22:40,959 --> 00:22:43,520
Liu Hong Yi was investigating Yu Lian's case...

311
00:22:43,520 --> 00:22:45,919
you were the one who told the Magistrate?

312
00:22:45,919 --> 00:22:49,955
That's why you became
an honored guest there today.

313
00:22:52,759 --> 00:22:53,759
Yes.

314
00:22:53,759 --> 00:22:56,040
I was the one who told Lord Li

315
00:22:56,040 --> 00:22:59,520
that Liu Hong Yi had rescued
the scholar who reported the case.

316
00:22:59,520 --> 00:23:01,280
That's why he gave me the token,

317
00:23:01,280 --> 00:23:04,242
so I could enjoy myself at Zhongxiao Pavilion.

318
00:23:06,120 --> 00:23:07,479
This... this is the token?

319
00:23:07,479 --> 00:23:09,399
I've really told you everything I know.

320
00:23:09,399 --> 00:23:11,330
I've held nothing back.

321
00:23:15,600 --> 00:23:17,367
You haven't explained everything yet.

322
00:23:17,367 --> 00:23:18,439
Keep talking.

323
00:23:18,439 --> 00:23:22,917
I told you! I've told you everything I know!
I really haven't held anything back!

324
00:23:24,120 --> 00:23:27,160
Do you think you can hide the truth
just because the victim can't testify?

325
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:30,159
Even if poison was used
to interrogate Liu Hong Yi,

326
00:23:30,159 --> 00:23:31,919
how did he get...

327
00:23:31,919 --> 00:23:34,640
all those external injuries?

328
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:37,479
- I...
- If you could find out the secret letter,

329
00:23:37,479 --> 00:23:40,919
wouldn't that be a great achievement
for you all?

330
00:23:40,919 --> 00:23:44,600
But Liu Hong Yi kept his mouth shut
no matter how much you tortured him.

331
00:23:44,600 --> 00:23:47,439
That's why you were willing
to hand him over to He Bo.

332
00:23:47,439 --> 00:23:48,867
I...

333
00:23:49,840 --> 00:23:51,800
You worked in the same office,

334
00:23:51,800 --> 00:23:54,520
yet you were so cruel to Liu Hong Yi.

335
00:23:54,520 --> 00:23:57,640
Was it truly because you had no choice
under your superior's authority,

336
00:23:57,640 --> 00:24:01,080
or can you simply not distinguish
right from wrong?

337
00:24:01,080 --> 00:24:03,880
Sir! Sir! I'm just trying to make a living
at the magistrate's office.

338
00:24:03,880 --> 00:24:04,953
Please spare me!

339
00:24:04,953 --> 00:24:06,399
Zhan!

340
00:24:06,399 --> 00:24:08,542
Don't be impulsive.

341
00:24:31,439 --> 00:24:32,919
Zhan,

342
00:24:32,919 --> 00:24:36,790
we will definitely find the truth
and clear Constable Liu's name.

343
00:24:37,399 --> 00:24:39,120
Within Xiangzhou's jurisdiction,

344
00:24:39,120 --> 00:24:42,183
there must still be many
honest and upright officials.

345
00:24:46,600 --> 00:24:49,320
I'm afraid it's already rotten to the core.

346
00:25:06,600 --> 00:25:08,161
Master Bai.

347
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:10,692
This way.

348
00:25:35,280 --> 00:25:36,719
You're working so hard on the case,

349
00:25:36,719 --> 00:25:37,960
yet you have to stay in a place like this.

350
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:40,120
Sorry for troubling you here.

351
00:25:42,240 --> 00:25:44,730
This room has everything we need.

352
00:25:44,730 --> 00:25:46,040
Besides,

353
00:25:46,040 --> 00:25:49,320
People like us who drift around treat the sky
as our blanket and the earth as our bed.

354
00:25:49,320 --> 00:25:51,355
Don't worry about it.

355
00:26:11,479 --> 00:26:13,040
Master Bai.

356
00:26:13,040 --> 00:26:14,330
The pharmacy is open.

357
00:26:14,330 --> 00:26:15,600
Go get some medicine quickly.

358
00:26:15,600 --> 00:26:16,679
I'll brew them for you.

359
00:26:16,679 --> 00:26:17,959
You certainly have many skills.

360
00:26:17,959 --> 00:26:21,030
Not only can you make hangover soup,
but you can also brew medicine.

361
00:26:21,030 --> 00:26:23,439
Yu Lian and I lost our parents early.

362
00:26:23,439 --> 00:26:25,640
We've supported each other since childhood.

363
00:26:25,640 --> 00:26:26,759
But come to think of it,

364
00:26:26,759 --> 00:26:28,580
as an older brother...

365
00:26:28,580 --> 00:26:30,360
I've been quite inadequate.

366
00:26:30,360 --> 00:26:33,479
Yu Lian suffered a lot because of me.

367
00:26:33,479 --> 00:26:35,530
I really owe her so much.

368
00:26:39,080 --> 00:26:41,586
It's a blessing for Yu Lian...

369
00:26:41,586 --> 00:26:43,360
to have a brother like you by her side.

370
00:26:43,360 --> 00:26:45,850
Don't talk about owing her anything.

371
00:26:54,679 --> 00:26:56,120
Alright, Master Bai.

372
00:26:56,120 --> 00:26:57,479
Go and get the medicine quickly.

373
00:26:57,479 --> 00:26:59,560
Otherwise, Lord Zhan will scold you
when he returns.

374
00:26:59,560 --> 00:27:01,422
Fine.

375
00:27:21,630 --> 00:27:22,730
[Ruzhen Embroidery Shop]

376
00:27:23,520 --> 00:27:25,257
Master Bai.

377
00:27:27,159 --> 00:27:29,077
Why are you here?

378
00:27:29,719 --> 00:27:32,919
Shen Zhong Yuan's crazed state
after being poisoned...

379
00:27:32,919 --> 00:27:34,920
looks familiar, doesn't it?

380
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:37,630
The poison he has...

381
00:27:38,320 --> 00:27:41,813
is the same one you used
on my two sworn brothers, isn't it?

382
00:27:41,813 --> 00:27:44,360
How many others have you controlled
with this poison?

383
00:27:44,360 --> 00:27:46,719
It is called Yemotian Poison.

384
00:27:46,719 --> 00:27:49,880
Yesterday, I intended to use it on Zhan Zhao.

385
00:27:49,880 --> 00:27:53,679
Unfortunately,
I don't know what's so odd about him,

386
00:27:53,679 --> 00:27:55,780
but he didn't succumb to it.

387
00:27:56,600 --> 00:27:57,800
But no matter.

388
00:27:57,800 --> 00:28:00,640
I still have your two sworn brothers
in my hands.

389
00:28:00,640 --> 00:28:02,360
Are my bargaining chips...

390
00:28:02,360 --> 00:28:03,719
enough to you?

391
00:28:03,719 --> 00:28:05,040
What do you mean?

392
00:28:05,040 --> 00:28:09,030
If your two sworn brothers
don't take the antidote soon...

393
00:28:09,030 --> 00:28:11,600
I'm afraid they'll end up
just like Shen Zhong Yuan.

394
00:28:11,600 --> 00:28:14,255
The antidote that day was fake!

395
00:28:15,366 --> 00:28:19,399
I never said that what you found on me...

396
00:28:19,399 --> 00:28:22,479
was definitely the antidote.

397
00:28:22,479 --> 00:28:24,560
You've been away from Xiankong Island...

398
00:28:24,560 --> 00:28:26,199
for quite some time now, haven't you?

399
00:28:26,199 --> 00:28:29,808
The poison should be flaring up again.

400
00:28:30,679 --> 00:28:35,560
When you returned to Xiangzhou, you wrote
to Xiankong Island to let them, right?

401
00:28:35,560 --> 00:28:38,067
Your sister-in-law has already replied.

402
00:28:42,520 --> 00:28:44,692
I passed by the inn just now.

403
00:28:44,692 --> 00:28:47,192
So I picked up the letter for you.

404
00:28:58,560 --> 00:29:02,280
Master Bai, you can't be so stupid as to think
that teaching me a lesson on the street...

405
00:29:02,280 --> 00:29:04,942
will get you the antidote.

406
00:29:06,479 --> 00:29:08,399
What do you want me to do...

407
00:29:08,399 --> 00:29:10,555
to get you to give me the antidote?

408
00:29:11,360 --> 00:29:13,280
I want to know...

409
00:29:13,280 --> 00:29:15,719
what Zhan Zhao has found out.

410
00:29:15,719 --> 00:29:17,479
If you tell me,

411
00:29:17,479 --> 00:29:19,679
I might consider...

412
00:29:19,679 --> 00:29:22,305
giving you the antidote.

413
00:29:22,305 --> 00:29:24,840
Of course, you don't have to answer now.

414
00:29:24,840 --> 00:29:28,030
Come to Fenglai Pavilion at this time
tomorrow to find me.

415
00:29:28,030 --> 00:29:29,880
Then tell me...

416
00:29:29,880 --> 00:29:32,817
if you'll agree to my terms.

417
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:00,679
Lord Zhan, Miss Huo.

418
00:30:00,679 --> 00:30:02,467
You're back.

419
00:30:04,342 --> 00:30:06,545
This man is a clerk
from the Yicheng County office.

420
00:30:06,545 --> 00:30:08,442
You should have met him before.

421
00:30:09,442 --> 00:30:11,479
He revealed a lot of inside information
about Zhongxiao Pavilion.

422
00:30:11,479 --> 00:30:13,040
I'm afraid he'll be silenced if he returns,

423
00:30:13,040 --> 00:30:15,567
so I brought him here to hide for a bit.

424
00:30:53,120 --> 00:30:54,439
What are you doing?

425
00:30:54,439 --> 00:30:55,520
Don't bother.

426
00:30:55,520 --> 00:30:57,615
I won't say a word.

427
00:30:58,439 --> 00:30:59,959
Are you keeping quiet...

428
00:30:59,959 --> 00:31:02,399
because you think the people from
Zhongxiao Pavilion will come to save you?

429
00:31:02,399 --> 00:31:04,560
After tonight, if I don't show up,

430
00:31:04,560 --> 00:31:07,230
they will definitely send someone for me.

431
00:31:07,840 --> 00:31:09,480
Is that so?

432
00:31:10,520 --> 00:31:13,479
You don't seem to be that important to them.

433
00:31:13,479 --> 00:31:15,239
I am very important!

434
00:31:15,239 --> 00:31:18,040
Without me helping them
scout so many pretty girls,

435
00:31:18,040 --> 00:31:19,630
I--

436
00:31:28,560 --> 00:31:30,679
I'm afraid even if they come,

437
00:31:30,679 --> 00:31:32,730
it won't be to save you.

438
00:31:36,320 --> 00:31:39,205
Then... you mean...

439
00:31:39,205 --> 00:31:40,800
they will silence you.

440
00:31:40,800 --> 00:31:41,999
If I were them,

441
00:31:41,999 --> 00:31:44,120
I wouldn't believe that you were beaten,

442
00:31:44,120 --> 00:31:46,642
yet didn't reveal anything.

443
00:31:51,567 --> 00:31:53,439
Then... then...

444
00:31:53,439 --> 00:31:56,480
Then I'll tell you everything you want to know.

445
00:31:56,480 --> 00:31:58,120
Can you save my life?

446
00:31:58,120 --> 00:32:00,840
Whether your life can be saved isn't up to me.

447
00:32:00,840 --> 00:32:02,120
But I do know...

448
00:32:02,120 --> 00:32:04,439
that if you don't say anything now,

449
00:32:04,439 --> 00:32:07,479
and wait until you're in court to speak,

450
00:32:07,479 --> 00:32:08,719
it will be too late.

451
00:32:08,719 --> 00:32:10,160
I'll speak.

452
00:32:10,160 --> 00:32:11,600
I will.

453
00:32:11,600 --> 00:32:13,555
What do you want to know?

454
00:32:15,120 --> 00:32:16,440
Why does Zhongxiao Pavilion...

455
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:18,120
have two separate entrances?

456
00:32:18,120 --> 00:32:22,392
Any differences between the guests entering
from Fenglai Pavilion and the shop's backyard?

457
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:29,239
If you speak clearly,

458
00:32:29,239 --> 00:32:31,239
it might help mitigate your crimes,

459
00:32:31,239 --> 00:32:33,143
and lessen your suffering.

460
00:32:33,972 --> 00:32:35,680
Fine.

461
00:32:35,680 --> 00:32:37,390
I'll talk.

462
00:32:38,479 --> 00:32:42,759
Those entering from Fenglai Pavilion
hold iron tokens and are martial artists.

463
00:32:42,759 --> 00:32:45,960
Those entering from the shop's backyard
mostly arrive in sedan chairs.

464
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:48,080
Few people ever see their true faces.

465
00:32:48,080 --> 00:32:49,959
So I'm not sure about their identities.

466
00:32:49,959 --> 00:32:53,439
I only know they are distinguished guests
of Zhongxiao Pavilion.

467
00:32:54,439 --> 00:32:56,239
The tokens!

468
00:32:56,239 --> 00:32:58,320
Even their tokens are
different from everyone else's.

469
00:32:58,320 --> 00:33:02,280
Their tokens are divided into three types:
gold, silver, and bronze.

470
00:33:02,280 --> 00:33:05,840
Of course,
the gold tokens are the most prestigious.

471
00:33:05,840 --> 00:33:07,040
Every time...

472
00:33:07,040 --> 00:33:08,999
these guests show up,

473
00:33:08,999 --> 00:33:11,199
they spend very generously.

474
00:33:11,199 --> 00:33:12,640
So most of those girls...

475
00:33:12,640 --> 00:33:15,091
are bought by them.

476
00:33:20,679 --> 00:33:23,679
Do you know who these people are?

477
00:33:23,679 --> 00:33:24,959
I'm not sure.

478
00:33:24,959 --> 00:33:29,200
The seating in the hall is assigned
by gold, silver, and bronze.

479
00:33:29,200 --> 00:33:31,890
Those of us with ordinary tokens

480
00:33:31,890 --> 00:33:34,926
never get a chance to speak with them.

481
00:33:38,840 --> 00:33:40,159
You've been kidnapping girls...

482
00:33:40,159 --> 00:33:42,399
so brazenly in Xiangzhou,

483
00:33:42,399 --> 00:33:44,280
yet you were never caught?

484
00:33:44,280 --> 00:33:47,360
Zhongxiao Pavilion forbade me from
targeting girls from the local area.

485
00:33:47,360 --> 00:33:49,080
They were afraid that if it was too close,

486
00:33:49,080 --> 00:33:51,580
their families would come looking for them.

487
00:33:51,580 --> 00:33:55,040
Originally, I would go to Jiangnan.

488
00:33:55,040 --> 00:33:57,560
Kidnapping girls and bringing them here.

489
00:33:57,560 --> 00:34:00,759
But I had bad luck and ran into Master Bai.

490
00:34:00,759 --> 00:34:03,679
After he gave me a beating,
I didn't dare go back there.

491
00:34:03,679 --> 00:34:06,492
But Zhongxiao Pavilion was pressing me hard.

492
00:34:07,320 --> 00:34:10,692
That's why I scouted two girls
nearby to finish the job.

493
00:34:10,692 --> 00:34:12,780
One of them...

494
00:34:13,759 --> 00:34:15,840
was Yu Lian.

495
00:34:15,840 --> 00:34:18,178
You kidnapped my sister--

496
00:34:18,880 --> 00:34:20,530
Fan.

497
00:34:21,640 --> 00:34:23,692
Shameless!

498
00:34:28,320 --> 00:34:32,040
The relatives of those two girls all came
to the embroidery shop looking for them.

499
00:34:32,040 --> 00:34:34,505
I was scared to death back then.

500
00:34:34,505 --> 00:34:35,605
However,

501
00:34:35,605 --> 00:34:38,120
after so much time has passed...

502
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:41,155
I haven't heard of any major commotion.

503
00:35:21,973 --> 00:35:24,320
- What's wrong?
- Don't talk.

504
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:27,102
What's wrong with you?

505
00:35:27,900 --> 00:35:29,120
It's nothing.

506
00:35:29,120 --> 00:35:32,455
I'm checking how your wounds are healing.

507
00:35:32,455 --> 00:35:33,455
By the way,

508
00:35:33,455 --> 00:35:34,719
when I went to get the medicine just now,

509
00:35:34,719 --> 00:35:36,640
I saw that Ruzhen Embroidery
has closed its doors.

510
00:35:36,640 --> 00:35:38,120
I'm afraid it's not just the shop.

511
00:35:38,120 --> 00:35:41,200
After yesterday's incident, Zhongxiao Pavilion
will likely suspend operations too.

512
00:35:41,200 --> 00:35:43,679
If so, it will be even harder to investigate.

513
00:35:43,679 --> 00:35:45,000
Even if they suspend operations,

514
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:47,640
the people from Hanshui Palace
won't be able to stop.

515
00:35:47,640 --> 00:35:50,359
They must be busy dealing with
the fallout these few days.

516
00:35:50,359 --> 00:35:51,839
We'll stake out the embroidery shop.

517
00:35:51,839 --> 00:35:53,942
Watch their movements.

518
00:35:56,600 --> 00:35:58,480
As for you, don't go.

519
00:35:58,480 --> 00:35:59,759
Take your medicine and rest well.

520
00:35:59,759 --> 00:36:01,113
Keep an eye on Hua Chong,

521
00:36:01,113 --> 00:36:03,217
and take care of Fan.

522
00:36:11,230 --> 00:36:13,430
[Hanshui Palace]

523
00:36:22,679 --> 00:36:24,799
- Greetings, Granny.
- Greetings, Granny.

524
00:36:24,799 --> 00:36:26,600
Emissaries of Sun and Moon.

525
00:36:26,600 --> 00:36:28,719
You said you had something to report.

526
00:36:28,719 --> 00:36:30,400
What exactly is it?

527
00:36:30,400 --> 00:36:33,742
Last night, we encountered
Zhan Zhao at Zhongxiao Pavilion.

528
00:36:35,960 --> 00:36:37,931
Zhan Zhao?

529
00:36:37,931 --> 00:36:39,799
He's actually not dead?

530
00:36:39,799 --> 00:36:41,150
Not only is he alive,

531
00:36:41,150 --> 00:36:43,520
but he had help.

532
00:36:43,520 --> 00:36:46,199
Zhan Zhao's courage is indeed second to none.

533
00:36:46,199 --> 00:36:49,555
He even dared to barge into Zhongxiao Pavilion.

534
00:36:49,555 --> 00:36:51,520
He Bo has operated in Xiangzhou for years.

535
00:36:51,520 --> 00:36:53,145
His influence is not to be trifled with.

536
00:36:53,145 --> 00:36:54,719
If Zhan Zhao wants to solve this case,

537
00:36:54,719 --> 00:36:56,679
he'll have to suffer quite a bit.

538
00:36:56,679 --> 00:36:58,040
In He Bo's territory,

539
00:36:58,040 --> 00:36:59,400
if Zhan Zhao wants to investigate,

540
00:36:59,400 --> 00:37:01,440
he is truly fighting a lonely battle.

541
00:37:01,440 --> 00:37:04,388
- So I want...
- You want to help him?

542
00:37:06,679 --> 00:37:08,359
It's not that I want to help him.

543
00:37:08,359 --> 00:37:10,600
I just want to help Hanshui Palace.

544
00:37:10,600 --> 00:37:12,960
For a century,
Hanshui Palace has been renowned.

545
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:15,560
Now we've stooped to
associating with the likes of He Bo.

546
00:37:15,560 --> 00:37:18,199
Risking our lives for his filthy business.

547
00:37:18,199 --> 00:37:19,440
Over time,

548
00:37:19,440 --> 00:37:22,967
people out there will surely mock us for
aiding and abetting a villain.

549
00:37:25,033 --> 00:37:29,160
Zhang Yue, do you feel mistreated

550
00:37:29,160 --> 00:37:30,960
that I'm making you do these things?

551
00:37:30,960 --> 00:37:33,080
Zhongxiao Pavilion is in the flesh trade.

552
00:37:33,080 --> 00:37:34,920
They victimize women.

553
00:37:34,920 --> 00:37:36,280
As a woman myself,

554
00:37:36,280 --> 00:37:39,242
- how can I be their accomplice?
- Impudent!

555
00:37:39,242 --> 00:37:42,591
You are insulting me as well.

556
00:37:43,520 --> 00:37:44,879
I wouldn't dare.

557
00:37:44,879 --> 00:37:46,520
In the past,

558
00:37:46,520 --> 00:37:50,905
someone like He Bo wouldn't even be worth
a second glance from me.

559
00:37:50,905 --> 00:37:52,040
But...

560
00:37:52,040 --> 00:37:54,440
Chang Hong Bi is still missing.

561
00:37:54,440 --> 00:37:58,159
Zhang Yue, you should know what would happen
if we don't cooperate with He Bo,

562
00:37:58,159 --> 00:38:01,255
what would become of Hanshui Palace?

563
00:38:04,199 --> 00:38:06,960
Hanshui Palace's lifeblood
is in someone else's hands.

564
00:38:06,960 --> 00:38:10,199
We have no choice
but to be at their beck and call.

565
00:38:10,199 --> 00:38:11,799
As things stand,

566
00:38:11,799 --> 00:38:14,239
in this contest between Zhan Zhao and He Bo,

567
00:38:14,239 --> 00:38:16,319
there is no chance of Zhan Zhao winning.

568
00:38:16,319 --> 00:38:19,440
If you help him recklessly and He Bo finds out,

569
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:21,600
it won't just be your life at stake.

570
00:38:21,600 --> 00:38:24,839
The entire Hanshui Palace
will be implicated because of you.

571
00:38:24,839 --> 00:38:25,960
Zhang Yue,

572
00:38:25,960 --> 00:38:28,380
do you understand?

573
00:38:29,319 --> 00:38:30,920
I understand.

574
00:38:30,920 --> 00:38:33,159
Everything has its priorities.

575
00:38:33,159 --> 00:38:36,067
We must not lose the big picture
for the sake of small gains.

576
00:38:40,879 --> 00:38:41,879
Zhi Hua.

577
00:38:41,879 --> 00:38:43,359
You called for me so urgently.

578
00:38:43,359 --> 00:38:46,480
Is it because you have a lead
on the matter I assigned to you?

579
00:38:46,480 --> 00:38:47,560
Yes.

580
00:38:47,560 --> 00:38:49,239
We have already discussed it.

581
00:38:49,239 --> 00:38:54,319
To deal with Zhan Zhao, we must find out
exactly what bargaining chips he holds.

582
00:38:54,319 --> 00:38:56,120
There is one more thing.

583
00:38:56,120 --> 00:38:57,400
I find it suspicious.

584
00:38:57,400 --> 00:38:58,799
Liu Hong Yi is dead.

585
00:38:58,799 --> 00:39:00,480
When Zhan Zhao arrived this time,

586
00:39:00,480 --> 00:39:02,359
he didn't go to the Yicheng County Court.

587
00:39:02,359 --> 00:39:04,280
But how did he follow

588
00:39:04,280 --> 00:39:05,520
the clue of the secret letter

589
00:39:05,520 --> 00:39:08,886
and find our Zhongxiao Pavilion
in such a short time?

590
00:39:09,600 --> 00:39:10,879
These two...

591
00:39:10,879 --> 00:39:12,920
are the embroidery shop's
shopkeeper and servant.

592
00:39:12,920 --> 00:39:14,279
According to their confession,

593
00:39:14,279 --> 00:39:17,600
in the past two months,
Hua Chong kidnapped two girls near Xiangyang,

594
00:39:17,600 --> 00:39:19,199
and sent them to our Zhongxiao Pavilion.

595
00:39:19,199 --> 00:39:21,240
[Fan Yu Lian]
Coincidentally,

596
00:39:21,240 --> 00:39:24,400
their families both went
to the embroidery shop to look for them.

597
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:25,830
You mean this Yu Lian,

598
00:39:25,830 --> 00:39:28,080
and this...

599
00:39:28,080 --> 00:39:31,440
[Hui Dai]
Her stage name here is Hui Dai.

600
00:39:31,440 --> 00:39:33,555
She's from Qingyuan County.

601
00:39:33,555 --> 00:39:36,520
That Fan Yu Lian is from Yicheng County.

602
00:39:36,520 --> 00:39:38,799
I've been to the courts of both counties.

603
00:39:38,799 --> 00:39:41,159
Their families had both
reported the disappearances.

604
00:39:41,159 --> 00:39:44,279
The Qingyuan County Magistrate
was quite efficient.

605
00:39:44,279 --> 00:39:47,319
The person who reported it
was silenced on the spot.

606
00:39:47,319 --> 00:39:49,159
But the Yicheng County Magistrate...

607
00:39:49,159 --> 00:39:50,640
So slow and indecisive,

608
00:39:50,640 --> 00:39:54,148
allowing Liu Hong Yi to pursue the case.

609
00:39:55,839 --> 00:39:56,879
My Lord!

610
00:39:56,879 --> 00:39:58,279
Spare us, My Lord!

611
00:39:58,279 --> 00:39:59,667
My Lord! My Lord!

612
00:39:59,667 --> 00:40:01,239
Spare our lives, My Lord!

613
00:40:01,239 --> 00:40:02,679
My Lord!

614
00:40:02,679 --> 00:40:04,799
My Lord, spare us!

615
00:40:04,799 --> 00:40:07,679
My Lord!

616
00:40:07,679 --> 00:40:09,920
Well, this Yicheng Magistrate.

617
00:40:09,920 --> 00:40:13,239
It seems he fooled us all.

618
00:40:13,239 --> 00:40:16,530
I'm afraid Liu Hong Yi followed Yu Lian's case

619
00:40:16,530 --> 00:40:18,440
all the way to Zhongxiao Pavilion.

620
00:40:18,440 --> 00:40:19,480
Exactly.

621
00:40:19,480 --> 00:40:21,719
He has already confessed to this.

622
00:40:21,719 --> 00:40:23,520
After Liu Hong Yi died,

623
00:40:23,520 --> 00:40:28,080
he sent men to stake out
Yu Lian's house and Liu Hong Yi's house.

624
00:40:28,080 --> 00:40:30,199
He wanted to silence the informant,

625
00:40:30,199 --> 00:40:32,080
but he never caught anyone.

626
00:40:32,080 --> 00:40:35,600
I believe this person
has already been found by Zhan Zhao.

627
00:40:35,600 --> 00:40:38,679
It was also this person
who led him to the embroidery workshop,

628
00:40:38,679 --> 00:40:41,319
causing us all this trouble.

629
00:40:41,319 --> 00:40:44,560
Hua Chong has disappeared.

630
00:40:44,560 --> 00:40:46,960
I'm afraid he has fallen into
Zhan Zhao's hands.

631
00:40:46,960 --> 00:40:48,830
Xing Ze.

632
00:40:48,830 --> 00:40:53,400
Take some men and search all the ruined temples
and abandoned houses in Xiangyang.

633
00:40:53,400 --> 00:40:56,392
I don't believe we won't find those people.

634
00:40:56,392 --> 00:40:58,040
- Yes, sir.
- Zhi Hua.

635
00:40:58,040 --> 00:40:59,279
Interrogate Yu Lian.

636
00:40:59,279 --> 00:41:02,319
Find out if she has any relatives nearby.

637
00:41:02,319 --> 00:41:05,640
Zhan Zhao might be hiding there
with the others.

638
00:41:05,640 --> 00:41:09,520
Yes, please hand Hui Dai over to me as well,
Master.

639
00:41:09,520 --> 00:41:11,580
I have something to ask her.

640
00:41:31,960 --> 00:41:33,279
Why are you here?

641
00:41:33,279 --> 00:41:35,343
Is something wrong?

642
00:41:36,703 --> 00:41:37,799
I'm here to take over for Huo Xiao Mei.

643
00:41:37,799 --> 00:41:39,199
I'm not tired.

644
00:41:39,199 --> 00:41:41,839
Why do you look paler and paler?

645
00:41:41,839 --> 00:41:44,120
You haven't been taking your medicine?

646
00:41:44,120 --> 00:41:45,880
I...

647
00:41:57,719 --> 00:41:58,960
What are they carrying?

648
00:41:58,960 --> 00:42:00,905
Let's follow them.

649
00:42:08,359 --> 00:42:09,640
Judging by the figure,

650
00:42:09,640 --> 00:42:11,279
it looks like a woman.

651
00:42:11,279 --> 00:42:14,055
This fell out of that girl.

652
00:42:16,960 --> 00:42:19,440
Before that, if anyone picks you,

653
00:42:19,440 --> 00:42:21,667
give them this.

654
00:42:24,080 --> 00:42:25,655
You're not afraid of me anymore?

655
00:42:26,520 --> 00:42:27,942
No.

656
00:42:28,600 --> 00:42:30,980
I'll wait for you to come back and save us.

657
00:42:40,400 --> 00:42:43,159
Hanshui Palace used to be quite reputable.

658
00:42:43,159 --> 00:42:45,880
Now you've been reduced to
doing He Bo's dirty work.

659
00:42:45,880 --> 00:42:47,839
Harming an unarmed girl!

660
00:42:47,839 --> 00:42:49,400
If I don't kill you today,

661
00:42:49,400 --> 00:42:51,630
justice will not be served!

662
00:42:52,319 --> 00:42:54,640
This girl wasn't killed by our Hanshui Palace.

663
00:42:54,640 --> 00:42:57,040
Don't waste your time fighting with us.

664
00:42:57,040 --> 00:43:00,319
He Bo already knows how you
found the embroidery workshop.

665
00:43:00,319 --> 00:43:01,920
The people you should protect...

666
00:43:01,920 --> 00:43:03,882
must be hidden well.
